                "icon": "return",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_b7VcVz": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We want you to love what you ordered! If your new pieces aren't quite right, we’ve made our return process as simple as possible.<br/><strong>1. The Basics</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Return Window:</strong> You have <strong>14 days </strong>from the date of delivery to initiate a return or exchange.</li><li><strong>Condition:</strong> Items must be returned in their original condition: unwashed, unworn, and with all tags still attached. Items with makeup marks, perfume scents, or cigarette smoke will not be accepted.</li><li><strong>Exclusions:</strong> For hygiene reasons, earrings, bodysuits, and swimwear (if the hygiene seal is broken) are <strong>Final Sale</strong> and cannot be returned.</li></ul><p><strong>2. Your Options</strong></p><p>We offer three ways to resolve your return:</p><ol><li><strong>Free Exchanges:</strong> If you just need a different size or colour, the shipping is on us!</li><li><strong>Store Credit + Bonus:</strong> Choose store credit and we will add an extra <strong>5% bonus</strong> to your refund amount to use on your next find.</li><li><strong>Refund to Original Payment:</strong> A flat £<strong>4.50 restocking fee</strong> will be deducted from your refund to cover the cost of return shipping and processing.</li></ol><p><strong>3. How to Start a Return</strong></p><p>Contact us and a member of the team will respond within 48 hours. </p><p>Please include the items you wish to return and tell us why (this helps us improve our sizing!), in the contact.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
