              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "When will I get my order?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "question_mark",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_CiiDTX": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We will work quickly to ship your order as soon as possible. If the order in-stock, we strive to get them shipped within 2 business days of order being received. If it is expected to be longer, we will contact you. </p><p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive an email with further information. Delivery times vary depending on your location.</p>",
