            "accordion_row_KatrpN": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Where are your products manufactured?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "plane",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_PGMBJq": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Our roots and our production are a family affair. Every piece is designed and ethically manufactured in India, at a dedicated facility owned and operated by our own relatives. This unique setup allows us to maintain a direct, personal connection to the people making our clothes. Once finished, every item travels to our headquarters in the UK, where it undergoes a final, rigorous quality check before being sent to you.</p>",
